title: DDT Be Ambitious ~Autumn Battle Rhapsody~
overview: Be Ambitious ~Autumn Battle Rhapsody~ was a professional wrestling event produced by DDT Pro Wrestling (DDT) that took place on November 30, 2025 at Korakuen Hall in Tokyo, Japan, and was headlined by a double championship match between KO-D Openweight & DDT Universal Champion  Yuki Ueno and Challenger Super Sasadango Machine.
